uk.ac.ebi.pridemod.model

Interface PTM

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPTM, PRIDEModPTM, PSIModPTM, UniModPTM

    public interface PTM
    Interface for PTMs. The PTMs are described by Accession, Name and Delta Mass. yperez.
